data.title: Triangle Live Music
data.text:
Rock, Folk, Jam Band

Jake Dean Band (JDB) is a Soulful, passionate, and high energy climactic band. This multi-genre band is influenced by such artists as: The Grateful Dead, Dave Matthews Band, WSP, Pearl Jam, Phish, Ben Harper, and many more. With strategically composed setlists chalk full of fun transitions, crowd moving covers, and their original music, you are garunteed to be left in High Spirits after every show!
